title: Nutri Ninja® | Ninja® Blender Duo™ with Auto-iQ™ (BL640 Series)
description:
The Nutri Ninja® | Ninja® Blender Duo™ with Auto-iQ™ (BL640 Series) features timed, intelligent blending programs that do the work for you, no guesswork required. 

Our Pro Extractor Blades®   breakdown whole fruits and vegetables, ice and seeds, skins and fiber for nutrient and vitamin extraction.  

5 Auto-iQ™ settings feature intelligent blending programs that do the work for you.

See more information at www.NinjaKitchen.com
